Package: cockpit-caddy
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, cockpit
Description: Caddy reverse proxy management plugin for Cockpit
 A Cockpit plugin for managing Caddy reverse proxy from the Cockpit web
 interface. Configure port-based reverse proxying with automatic self-signed
 TLS certificates — no DNS or subdomains required.
 .
 Each service is accessible via its own HTTPS port. Requires Caddy with the
 Admin API enabled (default: localhost:2019).
